 Exit fullscreen mode




 Step 3: Configure

Add your API key to .env:

OPENAI_API_KEY=your_key_here

 Enter fullscreen mode


 Exit fullscreen mode


Add a script to package.json:

"bin": {
 "suggest-commit": "./index.js"
}

